        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrogenation reaction",
        "description": "在间歇式高压釜反应器中，使用Pd-SiO2催化剂，在340°C、3 MPa氢气压力、4小时反应时间的优化条件下，对海枣籽生物油进行加氢脱氧，生产绿色航空燃料和柴油范围内的烃类。",
        "text_snippet": "Hydro-deoxygenation of the Date seed oil is done... Autoclave batch-type reactor with mechanical stirrer, pressure and temperature controller is used for hydro-deoxygenation of Date seed oil. Initially, 30 ml of oil and a known amount of catalyst are loaded vessel and closed adequately to avoid any leakage and pressure drop... maintained at 3 MPa... temperature is set to increase with a heating rate of 5 °C/min up to desired temperature (350 °C)... reaction is allowed to run for four h... The reaction mixture consisting of oil product and catalyst is passed to centrifuge tubes to separate the catalyst and product liquid oil.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      }
    ]
